Cyber Update Des.2011\US-17661  Isis Love, Jessie Cox, Holly Heart, Juliette March and Kaylee Hilton

Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Totally non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, all broadcast live to members. Today's update is RD 1 of 4. This was November's live match now edited for your enjoyment!

Holly Heart and Kalyee Hilton take on Jessie Cox and Juliette March, in this amazing rough and tumble non-scripted Tag Team Match up. These girls held nothing back, this is nothing short of a brutal catfight with rules.

Don't miss this first edited round of what is sure to be a classic match.
